\n| length10         = 03:44\n\n| title11         = If The Woodlands Has Something To Say (\u758f\u6797\u5982\u6709\u8bc9)\n| note11           = Wen Qing's theme song\n| lyrics11        =  Zhong Wuyi \n| music11         =  Chen Yiming\n| arranger11      =  \n| extra11         = Gao Qiuzi\n| length11         = 03:53\n\n| title12          = Passing by the Deserted City (\u8352\u57ce\u6e21)  \n| note12           = Xue Yang's theme song\n| lyrics12        =  Zhang Ying\n| music12         =  Xia Heng, Deng Qiangzhong\n| arranger12      =  \n| extra12        = [[Charlie Zhou]] \n| length12         = 04:19\n\n| title13         = Lone City (\u5b64\u57ce)\n| note13           = Yi City group's theme song\n| lyrics13        =  Lin Qiao\n| music13         =  Yu Honglong\n| arranger13      =  \n| extra13         = Sun Bolun & Chen Zhuoxuan\n| length13         = 03:52\n\n| title14         = Youth Especially Cannot Be Bullied (\u6700\u662f\u5c11\u5e74\u4e0d\u53ef\u6b3a)\n| note14           = Youth group's theme song \n| lyrics14        =  Yu Ci\n| music14         =  Chen Yiming\n| arranger14     =  \n| extra14         = Zui Xue, Zheng Fanxing, Qi Peixin & Guo Cheng\t \n| length14       = 03:59\n\n| title15          = Inappeasable (\u610f\u96be\u5e73)\n| note15           = Jiang Yanli's theme song \n| lyrics15         = Cheng Yi, He Siwei\n| music15          = Lin Hai\n| arranger15       =  \n| extra15          =  Yin Lin\n| length15         = 04:14\n\n| title16          = Not In Vain (\u4e0d\u6789)\n| note16           = Group song\n| lyrics16        =   Yi Zhe Lian Xiao Zui Qing He\n| music16         =  Yin Lin\n| arranger16      =  \n| extra16         = Naomi Wang\n| length16         = 03:55\n\n| title17          = Eternal Separation (\u6c38\u9694)   \n| note17           = Jiang Yanli & Jin Zixuan's theme song \n| lyrics17         =  Lin Qiao\n| music17        =  Yu Honglong\n| arranger17      =  \n| extra17         = [[Lara Veronin]] & Fabien Yang\n| length17         = 03:37\n\n| title18          = Hatred in Life (\u591a\u6068\u751f)   \n| note18           = Jin Guangyao's theme song \n| lyrics18         =  Within_Yi Ming \n| music18        =  Luo Xizhun \n| arranger18      =  \n| extra18         = Zhu Xingjie\n| length18         = 04:25\n\n}}\n\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = ''The Untamed'' OST (\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u539f\u58f0\u97f3\u4e50\u4e13\u8f91) \n| type       = Soundtrack\n| artist     = Various artists\n| cover      =\n| released   = {{start date|2019|08|05}}\n| recorded   = 2018\u20132019\n| genre      = [[Soundtrack]] \n| length     = \n| language   = {{hlist|[[Chinese language|Chinese]]}}\n| label      = {{hlist|New Style Media|[[QQ Music]]}}\n| producer   = Lin Hai \n}}\n{{tracklist\n|title1=The Untamed (\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4)\n|length1=02:01\n|title2=Unrestrained (\u65e0\u7f81) \n|note2=Instrumental version\n|length2=02:33\n|title3=Wang Ji (\u5fd8\u673a)\n|length3=01:01\n|title4=Love Entanglement (\u60c5\u7275)\n|length4=01:59\n|title5=Lotus Pier (\u83b2\u82b1\u575e)\n|length5=02:08\n|title6=Maneuvering Dizi (\u5fa1\u7b1b)\n|length6=02:15\n|title7=Glacier (\u88c2\u51b0)\n|length7= 03:26\n|title8=Drunken Dream (\u9189\u68a6)\n|length8=03:27\n|title9=Burial Mound (\u4e71\u846c\u5c97)\n|length9=02:24\n|title10=Sadness (\u4f24\u60c5)\n|length10=03:01\n|title11=If Life Was Just Like When We First Met (\u4eba\u751f\u82e5\u53ea\u5982\u521d\u89c1)\n|length11=02:36\n|title12=Won't Regret (\u4e0d\u6094)\n|length12=02:47\n|title13=Night Scamper (\u591c\u5954)\n|length13=03:51\n|title14=Day and Night (\u5be4\u5bd0)\n|length14=01:26\n|title15=Song of Lucidity (\u6e05\u5fc3\u97f3\u00b7\u4e71\u9b44\u6284)\n|length15=05:10\n|title16=Rest (\u5b89\u606f)\n|length16=02:32\n|title17=Greenery (\u8349\u6728)\n|length17=02:33\n|title18=Yi City (\u4e49\u57ce)\n|length18=01:03\n|title19=Artful Child (\u72e1\u7ae5)\n|length19=01:44\n|title20=Sunshot (\u5c04\u65e5)\n|length20=02:28\n|title21=Unrestrained (\u65e0\u7f81) \n|note21=Piano version\n|length21=01:23\n|total_length=\n}}\n\nOn August 19, QQ Music announced that the sales for the soundtrack album had broke fifteen million copies, officially attaining the platinum certification. As of September 2019, the album was the highest-selling soundtrack album on the platform, and ranked #15 on the list of highest-selling digital album.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/2169129705/I37UtiOec|title=\u6218\u62a5\u6765\u88ad\uff01\u606d\u559cOST\u5408\u96c6\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4 \u53e4\u98ce\u97f3\u4e50\u4e13\u8f91\u300b\u4e8e\u5e73\u53f0\u8fd0\u8425\u52a9\u529b\u4e4b\u4e0b\u6210\u7ee9\u6590\u7136\uff01|date=August 19, 2019|website=QQ Music Weibo|language=zh|access-date=September 16, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824214427/https://www.weibo.com/2169129705/I37UtiOec|archive-date=August 24, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\nThe series has a 8.3 rating on [[Douban]];<ref>{{cite web|url=https://movie.douban.com/subject/27195020/|title=\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4 (2019)|website=Douban|language=zh|access-date=2019-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922150411/https://movie.douban.com/subject/27195020/|archive-date=2019-09-22|url-status=live}}</ref> and has the highest number of reviews for China dramas.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/331722552_99919418|title=\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b\u6210\u4e3a\u8c46\u74e3\u8bc4\u5206\u4eba\u6570\u6700\u591a\u7684\u56fd\u4ea7\u5267|date=August 5, 2019|website=Sohu|language=zh|access-date=November 4, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191104113456/http://www.sohu.com/a/331722552_99919418|archive-date=November 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The series accumulated a total of 6.8 billion views on Tencent, as of December 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://data.guduodata.com/show/detail?showId=13382|title=\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4|website=Guduo Data|language=zh|accessdate=2019-12-16}}</ref> One of the major reasons for the series' popularity is its faithfulness to the original novel.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/334184291_120113576|title=\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4  \u6765\u65e5\u65b9\u957f\uff0c\u540e\u4f1a\u6709\u671f|date=August 16, 2019|website=Sohu|language=zh|access-date=August 16, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816194325/http://www.sohu.com/a/334184291_120113576|archive-date=August 16, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=hit /> \nIt was praised by ''[[People's Daily]]'' for its \"wonderful presentation of Chinese characteristics\"; showcasing traditional cultural elements through exquisite costumes, traditional Chinese music instruments; as well as transmitting positive values such as courage, chivalry and love for one's country.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2019-06-28/doc-ihytcitk8219861.shtml|title=\u4eba\u6c11\u65e5\u62a5\u8bc4\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b:\u4e66\u5199\u56fd\u98ce\u4e4b\u7f8e\u4f20\u9012\u6587\u5316\u81ea\u4fe1|date=June 28, 2019|website=Sina|publisher=People's Daily|language=zh|access-date=June 28, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629140324/https://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2019-06-28/doc-ihytcitk8219861.shtml|archive-date=June 29, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> ''[[China News Service]]'' similarly highlighted the exquisite costumes and showcase of traditional etiquette, while also praising the suspenseful plot and well-connected storyline.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2019/06-28/8878208.shtml|title=\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b\u5f00\u64ad\u53d7\u8ffd\u6367\uff1a\u670d\u5316\u9053\u7cbe\u81f4 \u5448\u73b0\u4f20\u7edf\u793c\u4eea|date=June 28, 2019|website=China News Service|language=zh|access-date=June 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630065248/http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2019/06-28/8878208.shtml|archive-date=June 30, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Wang Yibo was initially criticized by viewers for his blank acting style in the first few episodes, which he later improved upon with the help of director instructions.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://k.sina.cn/article_5603488861_14dfe745d00100jwdk.html|title=\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b\u738b\u4e00\u535a\u5c61\u5c61\u906d\u9a82\uff0c\u9020\u578b\u6f14\u6280\u60f9\u4e89\u8bae\uff0c\u540e\u671f\u5374\u8d8a\u770b\u8d8a\u987a\u773c|publisher=Sina|accessdate=2019-12-29|language=zh}}</ref>\n\nThe show has also garnered significant exposure and popularity globally for its strong plot, well-rounded characters, and elaborate clothing, makeup and stage production.<ref name=global /> On top of it's popularity in China, the series garnered significant international recognition.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bustle.com/p/the-untamed-a-primer-on-the-chinese-drama-the-internet-is-obsessed-with-21791344|title=What To Know About 'The Untamed,' The Chinese Drama Twitter Is Obsessed With|last=Carvalho|first=Keyla|website=Bustle|language=en|access-date=2020-04-21}}</ref> ''Film Daily'' described the drama as a \"Global Phenomenon,\" and credited it for contributing to the increased presence and popularity of Asian content on popular streaming sites such as Netflix.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://filmdaily.co/news/the-untamed-cultural-barriers/|title='The Untamed' cracked seemingly permanent cultural barriers|last=Lusky|first=Bridget|date=2020-02-25|website=Film Daily|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-21}}</ref> It has a score of 9.8 on [[Viki (website)|Viki]] and 9.4 on MyDramaList, making it the highest-rated Chinese TV series on the platforms.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.cgtn.com/news/2019-10-30/Chinese-TV-series-copyright-trade-is-gradually-diversifying-LdvEjITEXK/index.html|title=Copyright trading areas and destinations of Chinese TV series are increasingly diversified|date=October  30, 2019|website=CGTN News|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110064036/https://news.cgtn.com/news/2019-10-30/Chinese-TV-series-copyright-trade-is-gradually-diversifying-LdvEjITEXK/index.html|archive-date=2019-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref> It ranked #36 on Tumblr's Top Live-Action TV list of 2019, becoming the first Chinese TV drama to ever enter the chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1172254.shtml|title=What\u2019s trending on China's Twitter-like Sina Weibo on Wednesday|date=December 4, 2019|website=Global Times|access-date=December 5, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205002152/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1172254.shtml|archive-date=December 5, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\nThe heroic story with modern values was said to have struck a chord globally, and helps promotes Chinese style and traditional culture to the world, leading to a wave of interest in Chinese dramas.<ref name=global>{{cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-untamed-becomes-top1-twitter-trending-topic-gaining-global-attention-300884408.html|title=The Untamed Becomes Top1 Twitter Trending Topic, Gaining Global Attention|date=July 13, 2019|website=PR Newswire|access-date=August 16, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816194322/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-untamed-becomes-top1-twitter-trending-topic-gaining-global-attention-300884408.html|archive-date=August 16, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1165167.shtml|title=Chinese drama \u2018The Untamed\u2019 gains following overseas|date=September 22, 2019|website=Global Times|access-date=September 25, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012111613/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1165167.shtml|archive-date=October 12, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=hit>{{cite web|url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1168331.shtml|title=Hit adaptation of Chinese \u2018boys\u2019 love\u2019 novel debuts on Netflix|date=October 29, 2019|website=Global Times|access-date=November 6, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106040014/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1168331.shtml|archive-date=November 6, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> \n\n===Economic effect===\n''The Untamed'' is said to be the highest-earning drama of 2019, bringing in profits of more than 97.87 million yuan (as of August 15, 2019), with earnings from fan meetings, concerts, streaming platforms, album sales and merchandise.<ref name=high /><ref name=yuan>{{cite web|url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20190815/20190815A06ED800.html|title=\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b\u5438\u91d19700\u4e07\uff0c\u4e3a\u4f55\u201c\u8150\u5973\u201d\u7684\u94b1\u6700\u597d\u8d5a\uff1f|date=August 15, 2019|website=Tencent|language=zh|access-date=November 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110054131/https://new.qq.com/omn/20190815/20190815A06ED800.html|archive-date=November 10, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAs VVIP members are allowed watch the final episodes of the show in advance, more than 2.6 million new and existing subscribers paid to unlock the function, generating more than 78 million yuan in profit. More than 1 million copies of the soundtrack album were sold. In addition, a merchandise store was opened in Taobao and official merchandise was sold, with earnings amounting to 1.17 million yuan.<ref name=yuan /> Other source of earnings include paying to unlock the full music video of \"Unrestrained\" in advance, as well as the Bazaar Magazine featuring both lead actors Xiao Zhan and Wang Yibo which sold more than 330,000 copies within three days, before exceeding 1.1 million copies.<ref name=ent />\n\nA special system was introduced by Tencent, where VIP members have to accumulate \"star points\" to get a better chance to get tickets to the fan meetings and concerts. More than 326.7 million people paid 30 to 50 yuan to view the live broadcast of ''The Untamed National Style Concert'' on Tencent Video. It is estimated that the platform has earned more than 100 million yuan in revenue. Tickets of the concert were sold-out in less than 5 seconds, and leftover tickets were also marked up to 150,000 yuan by ticket scalpers from the original price of 627 yuan.<ref name=conc>{{cite web|url=http://js.people.com.cn/n2/2019/1031/c360313-33490017.html|title=\u300a\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u300b\u5357\u4eac\u6f14\u5531\u4f1a\u9ec4\u725b\u7968\u7092\u51fa15\u4e07\u5929\u4ef7|date=October 31, 2019|website=People's Daily|language=zh|access-date=November 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110060531/http://js.people.com.cn/n2/2019/1031/c360313-33490017.html|archive-date=November 10, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=high>{{cite web|url=https://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2019-11-04/doc-iicezuev7040148.shtml|title=326.7\u4e07\u4eba\u4ed8\u8d39\u770b\u9648\u60c5\u4ee4\u6f14\u5531\u4f1a\u76f4\u64ad \u5e73\u53f0\u6536\u5165\u8fd1\u4ebf|date=November 14, 2019|website=Sina|language=zh|access-date=November 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105133914/https://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2019-11-04/doc-iicezuev7040148.shtml|archive-date=November 5, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinamusicbusinessnews.com/?p=2503|title=Behind the 150,000 RMB Concert Tickets|website=China Music Business}}</ref> \n\nIn overseas markets, Tencent announced in October 2019 that ''The Untamed'' had boosted WeTV's growth by 250 percent with an average of 1 million application downloads per month since the drama was first launched in June.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blognone.com/node/112591|title=Tencent \u0e40\u0e1c\u0e22 \"\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e21\u0e32\u0e08\u0e32\u0e23\u0e22\u0e4c\u0e25\u0e31\u0e17\u0e18\u0e34\u0e21\u0e32\u0e23\" \u0e14\u0e31\u0e19 WeTV \u0e42\u0e15 250%, \u0e22\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e14\u0e32\u0e27\u0e19\u0e4c\u0e42\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e14\u0e40\u0e09\u0e25\u0e35\u0e48\u0e22\u0e40\u0e14\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e25\u0e30\u0e25\u0e49\u0e32\u0e19|date=Oct 17, 2019|website=Blognone|language=th|access-date=November 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017151558/https://www.blognone.com/node/112591|archive-date=October 17, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blognone.com/node/112586|title=Tencent \u0e1b\u0e35 2020 \u0e40\u0e14\u0e34\u0e19\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e49\u0e32\u0e2d\u0e35\u0e40\u0e27\u0e49\u0e19\u0e17\u0e4c\u0e40\u0e01\u0e21 \u0e40\u0e1e\u0e25\u0e07 \u0e2a\u0e23\u0e49\u0e32\u0e07\u0e0b\u0e35\u0e23\u0e35\u0e2a\u0e4c\u0e44\u0e17\u0e22\u0e25\u0e07 WeTV \u0e10\u0e32\u0e19\u0e04\u0e19\u0e14\u0e39\u0e01\u0e25\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e44\u0e1b\u0e2d\u0e22\u0e39\u0e48\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e40\u0e21\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e08\u0e35\u0e19|date=Oct 17, 2019|website=Blognone|language=th|access-date=November 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017151535/https://www.blognone.com/node/112586|archive-date=October 17, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nResponding to the demand of sold-out fan meets in Thailand and China, in January 2020, the cast members embarked on a multi-city worldwide fan meet tour. Cities included Bangkok, Singapore, Ho Chi Minh City, Tokyo, Seoul, Macau, Kuala Lumpur, Toronto, Los Angeles, New York.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotpot.tv/news/the-untamed-cast-to-go-on-worldwide-fan-meeting-tour|title=The Untamed Cast To Go On Worldwide Fan Meeting Tour|website=Hotpot.tv | access-date=January 28, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Award !! Category !! Nominee !! Results !! Ref.\n|-\n| rowspan=2|The Third Internet Film Festival || Best Director || Chen Jialin || rowspan=2 {{won}} || rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/336338547_141588|title=\u7b2c\u4e09\u5c4a\u7f51\u5f71\u76db\u5178\u76db\u5927\u843d\u5e55\uff0c\u91d1\u7261\u4e39\u5956\u5404\u5956\u9879\u9010\u4e00\u63ed\u6653|date=August 25, 2019|website=Sohu|language=zh|access-date=August 26, 2019i|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826020239/http://www.sohu.com/a/336338547_141588|archive-date=August 26, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best New Actor || Zhu Zanjin \n|-\n|GQ 2019 Men of the Year\n|Breakthrough Actor of the Year\n|[[Wang Yibo]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dy.163.com